# =========================================================================
# direnv — auto-loads the flake devShell on cd
# =========================================================================
# Requires direnv + nix-direnv, provided by ~/.omni-nix → home/devshell.nix.
#
# `use flake` evaluates flake.nix#devShells.default and puts its tools on
# $PATH. nix-direnv caches the result, so this is instant after the first run.
#
# After editing flake.nix OR this file, re-authorise / reload:
#     direnv allow
# To force a re-eval after changing inputs:
#     touch .envrc && direnv allow     # or: direnv reload
# =========================================================================
use flake
